TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF(POSITIONNAME=$$STR_DUMMY_POSITION1 OR POSITIONNAME=$$STR_DUMMY_POSITION2 OR POSITIONNAME=$$STR_DUMMY_POSITION3,'',
IIF(BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'SGPAFA' AND BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'SGPAGY' AND BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'BRUAGY' AND BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'SGPPD' AND BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'BRUPD' AND BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'SGPIWH' AND BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'SGP_Multi_Channel' AND BUSINESSUNITNAME != 'BRU_Multi_Channel' , 'BU name is not correct. ','')||
IIF((V_PRE_BU='SGP' AND V_PRE_POSITION != 'SGT' AND V_PRE_POSITION != 'SGY') OR (V_PRE_BU='BRU' AND V_PRE_POSITION != 'BRT' AND V_PRE_POSITION != 'BRY'),'POSITIONNAME do not match with BU name. ','')||
IIF(ISNULL(GENERICATTRIBUTE1),POSITIONNAME||' does not provide agency code;','')||
IIF(ISNULL(GENERICATTRIBUTE2) ,POSITIONNAME||' does not provide leader code;','')||
IIF(ISNULL(GENERICATTRIBUTE3),POSITIONNAME||' does not provide district code;','')||
IIF(ISNULL(GENERICATTRIBUTE6),POSITIONNAME||' does not provide channel code;','')||
IIF( ( (ISNULL(CS_P_GA1) OR CS_P_GA1='') AND ( ISNULL(V_GA1_Agency_Position) OR V_GA1_Agency_Position='')),POSITIONNAME|| ' GA1 Agency_code do not exist ','')||
IIF( ((ISNULL(CS_P_GA3) OR CS_P_GA3='') AND ( ISNULL(V_GA3_District_Position) OR V_GA3_District_Position='')),POSITIONNAME||' GA3 District_Code do not exist ','') ||
IIF(SUBSTR(BUSINESSUNITNAME,LENGTH(BUSINESSUNITNAME)-2,3) = 'AGY' AND ( ((ISNULL(CS_P_GA2) OR CS_P_GA2='') AND ( ISNULL(V_GA2_Leader_Position) OR V_GA2_Leader_Position='')) ), POSITIONNAME||' GA2 Leader_Code do not exist ',''))||
IIF(ISNULL(PAYEESEQ),'Participant record do not exist in trueComp','')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_STAGEPOSITION.STAGEPOSITIONSEQ as STAGEPOSITIONSEQ, DECODE(CS_STAGEPOSITION.STAGEPROCESSFLAG,3,CS_GASTAGEPOSITION.GENERICATTRIBUTE20) as MD5, CS_STAGEPOSITION.POSITIONNAME as POSITIONNAME FROM CS_STAGEPOSITION LEFT JOIN CS_GASTAGEPOSITION ON CS_STAGEPOSITION.STAGEPOSITIONSEQ=CS_GASTAGEPOSITION.STAGEPOSITIONSEQ AND CS_GASTAGEPOSITION.PAGENUMBER=0

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT CS_POSITION.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE as EFFECTIVESTARTDATE, CS_POSITION.EFFECTIVEENDDATE as EFFECTIVEENDDATE, CS_POSITION.NAME as NAME FROM CS_POSITION WHERE removedate = to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND islast =1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
UPDATE IN_ETL_CONTROL SET TXT_KEY_VALUE=(SELECT LPAD(TO_CHAR(COUNT(*)),10,'0') FROM IN_ST_POSITION WHERE TXT_ERR_MSG IS NOT NULL AND TXT_ERR_MSG<>'1'), DTE_UPDATE_DATE=SYSDATE WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='POSITION_STAGE_RECORD_COUNT' and DEC_RUNNING_FLG='1';
COMMIT;

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: UPDATE IN_ETL_CONTROL SET TXT_KEY_VALUE=(SELECT LPAD(TO_CHAR(COUNT(*)),10,'0') FROM IN_ST_POSITION WHERE DEC_CHANGE_FLAG=1), DTE_UPDATE_DATE=SYSDATE WHERE TXT_KEY_STRING='POSITION_PRESTAGE_RECORD_COUNT' AND DEC_RUNNING_FLG=1; COMMIT;
